        "observed_type": "text",
        "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
        "text": "A1 Define a growing spiral in the plane to be a sequence of points with integer coordinates P0 = (O, O), P1, . . , Pn such that n ≥ 2 and:",
        "bbox": [
          0.1011764705882353,
          0.13515151515151516,
